    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到《猫的冲突》！</strong></h2>通过合并和物品，建立和加强一支具有独特能力的猫队。你的团队会取得胜利吗 #MadeWithGodot<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>买你的猫</strong></h2>从随机生成的商店购买猫来组建你的团队！从60多只独特的猫中挑选，每只猫都有自己独特的能力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/e48b103374c276d9503255a26c11e80b.poster.avif?t=1725648877\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/e48b103374c276d9503255a26c11e80b.webm?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/e48b103374c276d9503255a26c11e80b.mp4?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与其他球队作战</strong></h2>看你的猫和其他球队比赛！每一轮，面对许多敌人团体中的一个。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/137dbbd4c75bf95f8ce8169327bba54b.poster.avif?t=1725648877\" width=600 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/137dbbd4c75bf95f8ce8169327bba54b.webm?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/137dbbd4c75bf95f8ce8169327bba54b.mp4?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>提升团队</strong></h2>每场比赛后，提高你的团队！升级猫以获得更强的能力，重新定位你的猫以获得最佳的战略位置，并给它们提供物品和力量来提高它们的技能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/d5e5a522ffde47d70b621ebc6acb34fd.poster.avif?t=1725648877\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/d5e5a522ffde47d70b621ebc6acb34fd.webm?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082630/extras/d5e5a522ffde47d70b621ebc6acb34fd.mp4?t=1725648877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>其他功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>酷模式！</strong>-4种独特的游戏模式，提供不同的挑战！<br></li><li><strong>了不起的成就！</strong>-通过解锁80个蒸汽成就来展示你的猫队建设实力！</li></ul>",
